Author: thebitchybulimic
Text: I do like soup! I just go back and forth between being able to eat it, but if my mentality is I have to eat what he is, I’ll eat less, and that’s alright by me. Thank you!

Author: LisichkaYenotik
Text: The same thing happened to me when I moved country. IF was an absolute godsend because the country I moved to was FULL of carbs and fruit and veg was scarce in the winter (and let's be honest...in the summer). I've since moved back, but honestly, IF is great. And don't forget - soup can be cheap, filling and low calorie! I live on carrot and parsnip soup these days...
